<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - dạymạaⁿ tmnḥny qwẗ lḥyạty wfy ḍʿfy rwḥk sạkn fyạ wbyʿny

[V2]
 wʿwdk lyạ trfʿny ʿạly wslạmk jwh qlby yḥyy wyṭmny

[V3]
 1- ạydk tsẖfyny wrwḥk ymnḥ lqlby slạm nwrk yḥfṭny wṣlbk rfʿ ʿny ạlạlạm

[V4]
 wfy wqt ḥzny rwḥk yjy yʿzyny wfy wqt yạỷsy rwḥk dymạ yḥyny

[V5]
 wymlạny bạlslạm

[V6]
 2- ḥṣnk ḥạmyny wdymạ trfʿny fwq ạlṣʿwbạt klạmk ysẖbʿny wwʿdk ạbnk ạlyẗ ạlbrkạt

[V7]
 wạnạ ʿbdk tsmʿny wạṭlb ydyny ạlmwly wạnạ ʿbdk tsndny wfy ḍʿfy tmnḥ qwẗ

[V8]
 wtʿzyny ạltrnymạt

[V9]
 3- bqwẗ tʿdyny dymạ mn ạy ḍyq fy ạlṭryq qwtk tḥfṭny bqwẗ wạnt ạʿẓm ṣdyq

[V10]
 wfy kl ḥyạty ḥạfẓ wṣạyạk fy qlby wfy kl ạwqạty ạnt yạ yswʿ fy qlby

[V11]
 mhmạ kạn ạlḍyq</lyrics>
<title>dạymạaⁿ tmnḥny qwẗ lḥyạty</title>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10331</hymn_number>
</song>